 y78 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">separation from His Father. </div><div class="t m2bd x93 h19 y45a ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">On the cross we have the supreme </div><div class="t mf xaa h19 y45b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">example of sacrifice. When we </div><div class="t m41b xaa h19 y45c ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">recognize that Jesus did all this so that </div><div class="t m5e2 xaa h19 y45d ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">you and I can be saved, our hearts melt </div><div class="t m188 xaa h19 y530 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">in love. The suffering that Jesus </div><div class="t mca xaa h19 y45f ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">endured for us is called to mind by the </div><div class="t m196 xaa h19 y989 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">feet-washing service and the bread </div><div class="t m6d xc h19 y519 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and wine of the Lord&apos;s Supper. </div><div class="t m29b xaa h19 y51a ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m63 xaa h19 y463 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t md9 x56 h19 y534 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Son Became Man </div><div class="t m862 x56 h19 yc1 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Gal. 4:4, 5) </div><div class="t m65 xaa h19 y536 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t me x56 h19 y536 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Son Lived As Man </div><div class="t m89f x56 h19 y537 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Heb. 2:16, 17) </div><div class="t m67 xaa h19 y538 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m325 x56 h19 yca ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s Son Suffered and </div><div class="t m8a0 x56 h19 y539 ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Died As Man </div><div class="t m183 x56 h19 y53a ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 1:11) </div><div class="t m69 xc h19 y53b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m8a1 x56 h19 y53b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Symbol of Humiliation </div><div class="t m8c x56 h19 y53c ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 13:12) </div><div class="t m6b xc h19 y46b ff3 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="